{"tid":1296783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民做個好市民計劃","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:20:39.000Z","uid":134912,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"551ce2d2de8f44152f049646c482ce9fac9a8471","tid":1296783,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">全民做個好市民計劃</span><br />\n<br />\n如各位市民見到配備警察裝備（槍/警棍/手扣等）而該人沒有回應或出示委任證，即合理懷疑該人干犯冒警，非法持有槍械等嚴重罪行，<span style=\"color: gold;\">其罪行最高刑罰超過監禁一年，即有權使用101拘捕令，制服犯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</span><br />\n<br />\n情景演示：<br />\n該人不出示證件並混入警隊，[size=4<span style=\"color: red;\">]即向其他警員舉報</span>[/size=4]並施加壓力要求出示證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n該人混入人群，配備警察裝備但沒有委任證，二話不說取用101拘捕令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">壓倒該人並用索帶綁起，以防走犯。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n捉錯人時，大家一齊say sorry，我地履行緊好市民責任，但你又冇委任證，點知你係咪葉繼歡？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啊sir你都身有屎，唔係拉我啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n做個好市民，你我有責！<br />\n冒警人士可恥，混入警隊可疑！<br />\n嚴打冒警人士，守護香港法治！<br />\n綁多幾條以防萬一，走甩個犯法治盡失！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後重申五大訴求！我無野講！</span></span>"},{"pid":"880f5d577a759a7e2bd927a154e739a35c3666bc","tid":1296783,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b004ea0ab59bc3ef561302408c6dca7f8621e73c","tid":1296783,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c184dca845f1f11ec974df8b8d74e5d0a868e2c4","tid":1296783,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"880f5d577a759a7e2bd927a154e739a35c3666bc","tid":1296783,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"好市民都要「選擇性執法」既！"},{"pid":"4a8c3c7be117a596ddb3a914a1389e191fefacc9","tid":1296783,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5ff385fc44f3081af4e4e492d689582982ef4277","tid":1296783,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"推！ 好市民係時候還下手"}]}